Installation:
    git clone git://github.com/SaxonC/dotvim.git ~/.vim
    git clone https://github.com/gmarik/Vundle.vim.git ~/.vim/bundle/Vundle.vim (diffpath for windows)

Create symlinks:
    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc

Remove submodule
    Remove it from .gitmodules
    Remove it from .git/config
    git rm --cached <path-to-module>

Get submoudle
    git submodule init
    git submodule update
